## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture the full complexity of the Syrian Civil War. The conflict's ongoing nature means that new developments could alter the understanding of its causes. Additionally, the perspectives included are limited to those available in English-language sources, which may not fully represent the views of all stakeholders involved in the conflict.